							title="The small, sexist joke that became a big deal" >
							<img width="186" height="124" src="http://media.salon.com/2012/03/madhouse-186x124.jpg" class="attachment-sm_horizontal wp-post-image" alt="madhouse" title="madhouse" />						The small, sexist joke that became a big deal						</a>
					</h4>
				</li>
							<li>
					<h4>
						<a href="/2012/03/06/white_conservative_manhood_crisis/" 
							title="White conservative manhood crisis" >
							<img width="186" height="124" src="http://media.salon.com/2012/03/santorum_rush-186x124.png" class="attachment-sm_horizontal wp-post-image" alt="santorum_rush" title="santorum_rush" />						White conservative manhood crisis						</a>
					</h4>
				</li>
				</ul>
</div>
    </div>
